IN.IC: se uporaba kot sedanjik in pretekli deležnik.

sense.def:
Kadar vojska
overruns a country
, ji uspe v kratkem času zasesti neko državo.

seg.quote: The north was overrun by the advancing troops.

sense.def:
Kadar neko območje
is overrun with animals or plants
, je na njem preveč živali ali rastlin.

seg.quote: The city is overrun by rodents.

sense.def:
Kadar dogodek ali sestanek
overruns
, traja dlje, kot bi moral.

seg.quote: I think we've overrun our time, haven't we?
